snippet.title: v7.8 Planetary Rewind Trailer - Honkai Impact 3rd
snippet.description:
Honkai Impact 3rd v7.8 Planetary Rewind coming soon! New S-rank battlesuit Lone Planetfarer debuts!
Part 2 Main Story Chapter V: The First and Last War, featured event Wilderness Development Logs, version bonuses, and more exciting content to be released! Stay tuned!
